-clusters.\n    *   \"Congestions\" does not have sub-clusters.\n    *   \"Repeatable analysis\" does not have sub-clusters.\n\n*   **White boxes:**\n    *   \"Overall measure\" has sub-clusters \"Overall CO2 emissions\" (yellow) and \"Level of air pollution\" (yellow).\n    *   \"Area-specific measure\" has sub-clusters \"Level of air pollution\" (yellow) and \"Level of noise", "answer": [0], "metadata": {"type": "fill_in_the_blank", "sub_type": "how_many_clusters_have_clusters_within", "difficulty": "basic"}, "setting": {"model": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite", "temperature": 0, "flag_async": true, "max_completion_tokens": 512, "prompt_type": "only_question"}, "token_usage": {"prompt_tokens": 273, "thoughts_token": null, "completion_tokens": 512, "cached_content_tokens": null, "total_tokens": 785}}
